div.p:
The originals of— 
                        (1)

Bills of lading;
                        (2)

Invoices;
                        (3)

All previous correspondence with firms in the country to which the
                            goods are shipped;
                        (4)

Contracts;
                        (5)

Insurance policies;
                        (6)

An affidavit setting forth all the facts of the case.
